    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, top the<strong> baked</strong> <strong>Cantonese-style soy basa</strong> with the<strong> chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a handful of <strong>coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>baked rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle any<strong> remaining seasoned soy sauce</strong> from the dish all over</p><p>Let everyone dig in!</p>",
